Short summary for newcomers:1. Kurt Tay is being charged for Distributing Intimate Images Without Consent Under Section 377BE of the Penal Code in Singapore. He shared one sensitive video  and one sensitive photo  more than 30 times in his own Group Chat. We know that he also transmitted the video and photo to at least 2 individuals via private conversation.Â  Members and fans of his group chat have advised him to take down the videos and photos  but he said he did not give a dang fug and will continue to post more.2. On 17th Aug  Kurt has also received an expedited protection order and he has allegedly continuously breached the Court Orderdailyfor several months. The AGC has directed the SPF to further investigate whether Kurt has committed a crime under the Protection from Harassment Act (POHA).3.
